Description: linkedarc.net is a Linked Data compliant hosting service for archaeologically themed data. Currently- linkedarc.net hosts the data of a single project- the Priniatikos Pyrgos Archaeological Project. The Priniatikos data is modelled primarily using the [CIDOC CRM](http://linkedarc.net/ontologies/ecrm.php "CIDOC CRM") ontology and its type values link to various public vocabularies- such as the [FISH](http://datahub.io/dataset/fish-archaeological-objects-thesaurus "FISH  vocabularies")- [Getty](http://www.getty.edu/research/tools/vocabularies "Getty vocabularies") and [British Museum](http://collection.britishmuseum.org/ "British Museum vocabularies").
